{
  "stem": "11964.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But all we knew is that they suffered tremendous casualties because we saw those soldiers coming in near death, many dead.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we waited it out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We waited it out until the Russians returned for good.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When the Russians returned for good, after about a week or so, we decided that we have to plan our emergence into liberation.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, the entire episode of liberation, it was a very curious-- emotionally, psychologically, curious period.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no elation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no happiness.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We knew we were liberated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I felt, and I always repeated it-- we were liberated from sure death.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That we knew, that no one is out there who is going to want to kill us because we are Jewish.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Although, even in that, we were wrong.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because in 1946, in Poland, not from-- far from Busko, in a-- in a town named Kielce, K-I-E-L-C-E, where, in early 1946, people would be returning from concentration camps, from DP camps, and such, there was a pogrom where Poles killed returning, returning survivors of the camps.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we didn't know that that was any kind of a possibility.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So at the moment of liberation, we felt that we were liberated from that angst, from the anxiety, from the anguish of whether or not we can survive yet another day.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we were not liberated from life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We didn't know what life has in store for us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, there was such a chaos.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "People were coming and going.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "People didn't know where to go, whom to search for.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We wanted to know whether or not there was any chance to, to find our parents.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
